Addendum by James Suzuki, 06/05/2026
The Unofficial Forces of Corruption Patch consists of publically released
source code from Disney Interactive's STAR WARS: EMPIRE AT WAR.  EULA and
other related user-end contracts all state that all content is owned by
Disney Interactive, and no implication is made to the contrary.

The Unofficial Forces of Corruption Patch uses "The Unlicense" to clar-
ify nothing in STAR WARS: EMPIRE AT WAR is owned by its contributors.
All content is owned by Disney Interactive and The Walt Disney Company,
and is subject to those entities' terms and restrictions.

In the spirit of open-source projects, the developers and contributors of
the Unofficial Forces of Corruption Patch should be credited, as they are,
for example, in the file "_Readme.txt," because they are the building
blocks of this project's existence and have devoted free time and free
effort into improving the project.
